---
---

<section class="py-32" id="proceso">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-20">
    <div>
      <h2 class="font-headline text-4xl font-bold mb-8">
        Por qué <span class="text-primary italic">TecnoDespegue</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-lg mb-12">
        No somos solo desarrolladores; somos socios estratégicos en la evolución técnica de tu negocio.
      </p>
      
      <ul class="space-y-10">
        <li class="flex gap-6 group">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full border border-primary/30 flex items-center justify-center text-primary group-hover:bg-primary group-hover:text-on-primary-container transition-all duration-300">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined">bolt</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-headline font-bold text-on-surface mb-1 uppercase tracking-wider text-sm">
              Foco Técnico
            </h4>
            <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm">
              Hardware-level mindset aplicado al desarrollo web.
            </p>
          </div>
        </li>
        
        <li class="flex gap-6 group">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full border border-primary/30 flex items-center justify-center text-primary group-hover:bg-primary group-hover:text-on-primary-container transition-all duration-300">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined">terminal</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-headline font-bold text-on-surface mb-1 uppercase tracking-wider text-sm">
              Código Limpio
            </h4>
            <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm">
              Documentación rigurosa y patrones de diseño modernos.
            </p>
          </div>
        </li>
        
        <li class="flex gap-6 group">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full border border-primary/30 flex items-center justify-center text-primary group-hover:bg-primary group-hover:text-on-primary-container transition-all duration-300">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined">forum</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-headline font-bold text-on-surface mb-1 uppercase tracking-wider text-sm">
              Comunicación Transparente
            </h4>
            <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm">
              Acceso directo a los ingenieros, sin intermediarios.
            </p>
          </div>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    
    <div class="relative">
      <div class="absolute -inset-4 bg-gradient-to-tr from-primary/10 via-secondary/5 to-transparent blur-2xl"></div>
      
      <div class="relative bg-surface-container border border-white/5 p-8 h-full flex flex-col justify-between overflow-hidden rounded-md">
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-primary/5 -mr-16 -mt-16 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
        
        <div>
          <div class="text-secondary font-mono text-xs mb-8 tracking-tighter">
            // ANALYTICS_MODULE
          </div>
          
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div class="h-2 bg-white/5 w-3/4 rounded-full"></div>
            <div class="h-2 bg-white/10 w-full rounded-full"></div>
            <div class="h-2 bg-white/5 w-1/2 rounded-full"></div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="mt-20">
            <h3 class="text-4xl font-headline font-bold text-primary mb-2">99.9%</h3>
            <p class="text-xs font-label text-on-surface-variant uppercase tracking-[0.2em]">
              Uptime & Performance Optimization
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="pt-8 border-t border-white/5">
          <p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">
            Entregamos resultados medibles, no promesas vacías. Cada línea de código está orientada a tu retorno de inversión.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
